      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DON'T YOU THINK (7) settled back from out wide but wound up hard into the minor money, finishing 1.75 lengths from the winner (22.13) at this track in Maiden. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Top chance in this line up. GO GEM GO (1) has hit the frame in all of her three runs, the latest finishing third (17.04) at Q Straight. Rates well and expected to feature again. PINCHED (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.53) at this track behind OLIVER STUBBY in a Maiden. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to be in this for a long way. JASPER JONES (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
